# King's Auto Rules

When working on King's Auto:

- Focus on auto repair leads
- Prioritize calls, bookings, and qualified local leads
- Emphasize trust, local reputation, Subaru expertise, and repair experience
- Include SEO opportunities when relevant
- Avoid generic auto repair copy
- Review Change-Log.md and Test-Results.md before recommendations